- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also a likely category as R-MAT is often used to model social networks and information networks. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is another possible category as R-MAT is used to generate network graphs. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as R-MAT can be used to model systems and control networks. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes an algorithmic improvement for generating R-MAT graphs.
